Groundwater
===========

.. currentmodule:: aquacrop

Configuration
~~~~~~
.. code-block:: python

   [GROUNDWATER]
   water_table = false
   variable_water_table = false
   filename
   

Options
~~~
``filename`` : ``str``
    Path to netCDF file containing the meteorological input variable.

``varname`` : ``str``
    NetCDF variable name.
